The [[Flask with Lemon Sirup|Lemon Sirup]] is one of 3 different sirups used in part of the [[Threatened Dreams Quest#Sweet Dreams|Sweet Dreams Quest]] which are later applied to the [[Gingerbread Key]]. 

To make this sirup you must combine [[Sugar (Quest)]] {{Ilink|Sugar (Quest)}} and a [[Lemon]]. {{Ilink|Lemon}}

If you wish to make additional sirups for decoration or to create multiple [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)|Gingerbread Key]]s, {{Ilink|Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)}} you '''must remain at this stage of the quest''' until you have gathered as many as you need. Once you progress past this part of the quest, you will no longer be able to collect the 3 [[Sugar (Quest)|Sugar Cubes]] each hour.

The [[Flask with Moon Melon Sirup|Moon Melon Sirup]] is one of 3 different sirups used in part of the [[Threatened Dreams Quest#Sweet Dreams|Sweet Dreams Quest]] which are later applied to the [[Gingerbread Key]]. 

To make this sirup you must combine [[Sugar (Quest)]] {{Ilink|Sugar (Quest)}} and a [[Moon Melon]]. {{Ilink|Moon Melon}}

If you wish to make additional sirups for decoration or to create multiple [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)|Gingerbread Key]]s, {{Ilink|Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)}} you '''must remain at this stage of the quest''' until you have gathered as many as you need. Once you progress past this part of the quest, you will no longer be able to collect the 3 [[Sugar (Quest)|Sugar Cubes]] each hour.

The [[Flask with Raspberry Sirup|Raspberry Sirup]] is one of 3 different sirups used in part of the [[Threatened Dreams Quest#Sweet Dreams|Sweet Dreams Quest]] which are later applied to the [[Gingerbread Key]]. 

To make this sirup you must combine [[Sugar (Quest)]] {{Ilink|Sugar (Quest)}} and a [[Raspberry]]. {{Ilink|Raspberry}}

If you wish to make additional sirups for decoration or to create multiple [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)|Gingerbread Key]]s, {{Ilink|Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)}} you '''must remain at this stage of the quest''' until you have gathered as many as you need. Once you progress past this part of the quest, you will no longer be able to collect the 3 [[Sugar (Quest)|Sugar Cubes]] each hour.

The [[Gingerbread Key]] is used in the [[Threatened Dreams Quest#Sweet Dreams|Threatened Dreams Quest - Sweet Dreams]] and undergoes several transformations with different sirups. These transformations are as follows:

* First Stage: Using a [[Flask with Moon Melon Sirup]] {{Ilink|Flask with Moon Melon Sirup}} on the [[Gingerbread Key]] will change it to a [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon)|Gingerbread Key with Moon Melon]]. {{Ilink|Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon)}}

* Second Stage: Using a [[Flask with Raspberry Sirup]] {{Ilink|Flask with Raspberry Sirup}} on the [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon)]] will change it to a [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon and Raspberry)|Gingerbread Key with Moon Melon and Raspberry]]. {{Ilink|Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon and Raspberry)}}

* Final Stage: Using a [[Flask with Lemon Sirup]] {{Ilink|Flask with Lemon Sirup}} on the [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon and Raspberry)]] will change it to a [[Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)|Gingerbread Key with Moon Melon, Raspberry, and Lemon]]. {{Ilink|Gingerbread Key (Moon Melon, Raspberry and Lemon)}}.

To create these sirups, you must combine [[Sugar (Quest)|Sugar]] {{Ilink|Sugar (Quest)}} with a [[Moon Melon]], {{Ilink|Moon Melon}} a [[Raspberry]], {{Ilink|Raspberry}} and a [[Lemon]], {{Ilink|Lemon}} respectively. This will yield a [[Flask with Moon Melon Sirup]], {{Ilink|Flask with Moon Melon Sirup}} a [[Flask with Raspberry Sirup]], {{Ilink|Flask with Raspberry Sirup}} and a [[Flask with Lemon Sirup]], {{Ilink|Flask with Lemon Sirup}} which are used on the key in that specific order.

